  "text": "Difficult and traumatic life events are known to play an important role in the development of AN, and it has been emphasized that in males psychosocial life events have a more prominent place in the emergence of AN than in females [CITATION_1] . The medical problems and treatment difficulties experienced by our patient are thought to have played a role in the emergence of AN.",
